g.text: "US1013 - Rank the candidates for a job opening" Sequence Diagram
Asks to rank all candidates of a JobOpening
Shows the list of the jobOpenings to choose
Choose the JobOpening to list all of their candidates
Shows the list of the candidates filtered by jobOpening
Ask to choose the candidates you want to rank
Choose one or more candidates to rank
Ask to choose the positions you want to put the candidates
Choose the respective positions of the candidates
Shows the list of the candidates with the new ranks
Choose the option to end the ranking process and save
